QuestData.Title: The Highlord Calls
QuestData.Description:
A messenger from Oribos has informed us that Highlord Fordragon has requested your presence in Oribos.
It seems it pertains to the Maw... and the Master's plans, no doubt.
I suggest you heed his summons, Maw Walker. We must leave nothing to chance.
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to Highlord Bolvar Fordragon in Oribos.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Report to Highlord Bolvar Fordragon in Oribos.
